headline: Mehmet Oz is a Phony Conservative.
author: Sarah Hoyt
sentences: The only thing I don't like about Trump, the President, was he punched ways too beneath his rank and raised his enemies' status.
He governed as a conservative because the other groups were off their rockers and couldn't stop vilifying him.
He was nominated with the help of Democrats who believed he was the only candidate that Hillary could beat.
Oz, like Trump, already has the buck, may be he would turn into another Trump.
In any case, how many "conservatives" remained conservative in the Swamp?
Politicians work for themselves for the power and the buck.
The biggest mistake he made was to endorse Snake Romney.
DeSantis would fight and keep his presidential dignity.
He shows real conservatives how to fight back.
Barr was the only one who would take the job.
